 can see she has tried to educate herself on the topic before saying things.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/standuptothegrownups.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/IMG-4222.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-223\" width=\"317\" height=\"311\" srcset=\"https:\/\/standuptothegrownups.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/IMG-4222.png 497w, https:\/\/standuptothegrownups.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/IMG-4222-300x294.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 317px) 100vw, 317px\" \/><figcaption>Here, the black censor feels cornered, and said a very bold statement. &#8220;There has never been any genocide in this country [Australia] ever&#8221;. Never feel pressured into saying things that you cannot defend.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/standuptothegrownups.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/IMG-4223.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-224\" width=\"364\" height=\"671\" srcset=\"https:\/\/standuptothegrownups.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/IMG-4223.png 534w, https:\/\/standuptothegrownups.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/IMG-4223-163x300.png 163w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 364px) 100vw, 364px\" \/><figcaption>Here my friend is arguing using evidence. This is extremely important.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/standuptothegrownups.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/IMG-4224-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-241\" width=\"323\" height=\"249\" srcset=\"https:\/\/standuptothegrownups.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/IMG-4224-1.png 504w, https:\/\/standuptothegrownups.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/IMG-4224-1-300x231.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 323px) 100vw, 323px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/standuptothegrownups.net\/wp-