t I just wanted to label things. I also do not think that he knew that I was 13 then.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/standuptothegrownups.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/IMG-4235.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-237\" width=\"419\" height=\"619\" srcset=\"https:\/\/standuptothegrownups.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/IMG-4235.png 634w, https:\/\/standuptothegrownups.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/IMG-4235-203x300.png 203w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 419px) 100vw, 419px\" \/><figcaption>After this, the black censor did not reply, so the conversation ended.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>I had this conversation on the Prime Minister&#8217;s instagram account after he told people not to go to the Black Lives Matter protests in June 2020. It is very long but I have included it in full with some comments on each person&#8217;s arguments. In summary, though, I said this country was founded on genocide, [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[9],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/standuptothegrownups.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/205"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/standuptothegrownups.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/standuptothegrownups.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/standuptothegrownups.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/standuptothegrownups.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=205"}],"version-history":[{"count":7,"href":"https:\/\/standuptothegrownups.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/205\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":244,"href":"https:\/\/standuptothegrownups.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/205\/revisions\/244"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https: